name: Tribute to "Nicolas Bets" through the windows #2
description:
Tribute to "Nicolas Bets" through the windows.
Nicolas Bets est un artiste, photographe mondialement connu, allez voir son blog et vous verrez l'immensité de son travail! https://www.nicolasbets.com/
 
J'adore ses photos et encore plus l'homme qu'il est malgré sa renommée, vous avez toujours un bonjour et il RT toujours vos publications.
Savoir garder du respect envers les "petits" quand on est connu est un signe que vous êtes un grand homme! Merci Nico.

Nicolas Bets is a world famous artist and photographer, check out his blog and you will see the immensity of his work! https://www.nicolasbets.com/
 
I love his photos and even more the man he is despite his fame, you always have a hello and he always sends you posts.
Knowing how to respect the "little ones" when you are known is a sign that you are a great man! Thanks Nico.
